metadata.name: #01 - Elf Castle
metadata.description:
Elf Castle - 360° showcase, 1/1

The Elf Castle will have 101 immersive tree houses in the future for users to hang out in the metaverse. The first owner of this art work will later gain access to a virtual tour of their tree house, and will receive exclusive benefits during the launch of the 101 immersive NFT collection of this variant.

1800 x 2000 pixels

 More info: https://www.thinkhuma.com/
